      <title>德国保守党誓言加大强硬移民政策力度</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/german-conservatives-vow-to-intensify-hard-line-immigration-push</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国保守派反对党领袖弗里德里希·梅尔茨誓言要推动强硬的移民法案在议会获得通过，加大力度在下个月的提前选举之前吸引选民脱离极右翼德国选择党。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/german-conservatives-vow-to-intensify-hard-line-immigration-push</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 Jan 2025 14:47:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普的援助令可能危及非洲人民的生命和美国影响力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/trump-s-aid-order-seen-risking-lives-and-us-influence-in-africa</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国际援助组织警告称，特朗普政府对外国援助的“停工令”不仅危及生命，还将影响美国在非洲的影响力。美国的援助资金涵盖了从军事演习到当地医院等一切领域。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/trump-s-aid-order-seen-risking-lives-and-us-influence-in-africa</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 Jan 2025 14:43:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
